id: memory_layout_legacy_hal
label: "Toolchain: Legacy HAL Compatible Memory Layout"
package: platform
description: >
  This component is meant to be used only in cases where an application
  specifically needs to have a memory layout which matches the previous
  releases of the flex/zigbee/connect sdk memory layout. This affects
  the placement of the nvm storage section when using an internal storage
  bootloader.
category: Platform|Toolchain
quality: production
root_path: platform/common
provides:
  - name: memory_layout_legacy_hal
